<p class="BubbleTitleSub">Campaign of Collaboration, an Enduring Dialogue with Industry</p>
<p>By Chief, Training & Industry Collaboration Branch, Science and Technology Division, Concept Development and Learning Directorate (CDLD), Army Capabilities Integration Center (ARCIC), May 21, 2015</p>
