			<div class="blockcaption" id="cap320">ARCIC Director Lt. Gen. H.R. McMaster provided remarks to a cross section of industry representatives and participants from previous Technology Information Exchanges (TIE) and cut a commemorative cake with Mr. Timothy Winter, Vice President, Northrop Grumman Information Systems.</div>
